data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This updated 4-bed, 1-bath modern townhome is a true gem in a highly sought-after neighborhood. Step into a world of modern elegance with crisp and clean design throughout. The heart of the home is the brand-new open concept kitchen, featuring pristine white shaker cabinets, top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances, recessed lighting, granite countertops, and luxurious LVP flooring. The first floor seamlessly blends a spacious dining area with a light-filled living room, courtesy of large windows that bathe the space in natural light.Venture to the second floor, where you'll discover three generously sized bedrooms, each boasting ample closet space. The newer luxurious hall bath provides a touch of sophistication and comfort. The lower level presents a finished basement, freshly painted and adorned with carpeting. This level also hosts a convenient separate laundry room, ensuring both functionality and style. The garage has been transformed into a versatile bonus room, awaiting the personal touch of its new owner. The gleaming refinished hardwood floors and a modern color palette throughout the entire home create an inviting atmosphere. Schedule your showing today and envision the lifestyle that awaits in this beautifully updated townhome.
